Class SingleWebCmsComponentFormProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.processors.EntityViewProcessorAdapter
      • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.processors.SaveEntityViewProcessor
        • com.foreach.across.modules.webcms.domain.component.web.SingleWebCmsComponentFormProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.EntityViewProcessor

    @Component
public class SingleWebCmsComponentFormProcessor
extends com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.processors.SaveEntityViewProcessor
    Layouts the web component form pages, builds the actual component model and renders the form. Mainly intended for indirect use by the WebCmsObjectComponentViewsConfiguration. See the WebCmsComponentsFormProcessor if you want to add the ability to edit a certain component to another form page.
    Since:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
    WebCmsComponentsFormProcessor, WebCmsObjectComponentViewsConfiguration
